drm/bridge: nwl-dsi: Drop DRM_BRIDGE_ATTACH_NO_CONNECTOR check.

We don't create a connector but let panel_bridge handle that so there's
no point in rejecting DRM_BRIDGE_ATTACH_NO_CONNECTOR.

